OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FMoves to create pensions "mega funds"
OL,8,Fcould lead to power being concentrated
OL,9,Fin the hands of a small number of
OL,10,Fpeople, a report has warned.
OL,12,FThe "pensions powerbrokers" research
OL,13,Ffrom consultants LCP (Lane Clark &
OL,14,FPeacock) estimated that more than half
OL,15,Fof the money in occupational defined
OL,16,Fcontribution (DC) pensions ` over #160
OL,17,Fbillion ` is controlled by fewer than
OL,18,F50 trustees.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@eO]tD@EOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FThe report said: "We are witnessing an
OL,8,Fextraordinary consolidation of power
OL,9,Finto the hands of a remarkably small
OL,10,Fnumber of people."
OL,12,FIt warned that a drive towards huge
OL,13,Ffunds, where schemes typically serve
OL,14,Fthousands of employers and millions of
OL,15,Fworkers, risks a loss of employer and
OL,16,Fmember voices in the running of
OL,17,Fschemes.
OL,26,@oD@ROUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FIt said issues also raised include
OL,8,Fwhere sources of innovation might come
OL,9,Ffrom in a pension landscape "dominated
OL,10,Fby a handful of giant players".
OL,12,FThe report said there are 11 million
OL,13,Fextra workplace pension savers
OL,14,Fcompared with 2012 when automatic
OL,15,Fenrolment started, overwhelmingly in
OL,16,FDC schemes.
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FWith DC schemes, savers bear the risk
OL,8,Fof the eventual size of their
OL,9,Fretirement pot, based on factors such
OL,10,Fas investment performance and
OL,11,Fcontributions.
OL,13,FThe report said: "Prior to the start
OL,14,Fof automatic enrolment, the dominant
OL,15,Fform of workplace occupational pension
OL,16,Fprovision was the single employer
OL,17,FTrust. These are schemes designed to
OL,18,Fprovide pensions purely for the
OL,19,Fpresent and past employees of a single
OL,20,Femployer."
OL,26,@uD@ROU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FThe number of occupational trust-based
OL,8,FDC pension schemes tied to a single
OL,9,Femployer has been in decline, while
OL,10,Fmulti-employer "master trusts" have
OL,11,Fgrown "rapidly" in recent years, the
OL,12,Freport said.
OL,14,FSir Steve Webb, a former Liberal
OL,15,FDemocrat pensions minister, who is now
OL,16,Fa partner at LCP, said: "The
OL,17,Fincreasing concentration of power in
OL,18,Fthe hands of a small number of
OL,19,Ftrustees is extraordinary.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@^O]sD@GOUsD@OO]xD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"Whilst these individuals will be
OL,8,Fcarefully chosen and typically highly
OL,9,Fexpert, the model of having a handful
OL,10,Fof people overseeing huge 'mega funds'
OL,11,Fraises serious questions which the
OL,12,FGovernment has not so far addressed.
OL,14,F"In particular, much more needs to be
OL,15,Fdone to make sure that there is proper
OL,16,Faccountability of trustees by
OL,17,Femployers and scheme members, and that
OL,18,Fthere is scope for innovation and
OL,19,Fchallenge in these enormous financial
OL,20,Finstitutions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FThe report was based on analysis of
OL,8,Fdata on scheme assets, alongside
OL,9,Finterviews with industry figures,
OL,10,Fincluding trustees and providers of
OL,11,FMaster Trusts.
OL,13,FLCP partner Nathalie Sims said: "There
OL,14,Fis no doubt that the way pension
OL,15,Fschemes are run will benefit from the
OL,16,Fcurrent drive to greater
OL,17,Fprofessionalisation of trusteeship.
OL,26,@uD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"In particular, overseeing
OL,8,Fmultibillion-pound pension schemes
OL,9,Frequires a highly skilled group of
OL,10,Fpeople, with access to ongoing
OL,11,Ftraining and support.
OL,13,F"But it is also important that we have
OL,14,Fstructures in place to make sure that
OL,15,Fthere is plenty of independent
OL,16,Fchallenge and advice for these 'mega
OL,17,Ffund' trustees, as well as diversity
OL,18,Fof thought amongst those who secure
OL,19,Fthese crucial roles in the future of
OL,20,Fworkplace pensions in Britain."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FHelen Dean, chair of the Standard Life
OL,8,FMaster Trust Board, said: "The
OL,9,Fconcentration of decision-making power
OL,10,Fshould not be perceived as a negative.
OL,12,F"On the contrary, such configurations
OL,13,Fare easier to observe and open to
OL,14,Fhigher levels of scrutiny than the
OL,15,Fhundreds of single employer trusts
OL,16,Fcurrently operating.
OL,26,@pD@[OUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"The decisions taken by the mega funds
OL,8,Fwill be some of the most publicly
OL,9,Fscrutinised, underpinned by the
OL,10,Fstrongest governance, extensive
OL,11,Fsupport structures, and undertaken by
OL,12,Fhighly qualified individuals with deep
OL,13,Fexperience built-up over many years.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"Though we're at the start of this
OL,8,Fconsolidation mega fund journey in the
OL,9,FUK, we must stay focused on the
OL,10,Fopportunity to raise the bar to
OL,11,Fdeliver better outcomes for members
OL,12,Facross the board, and this includes
OL,13,Fwelcoming heightened levels of
OL,14,Fprofessional governance and oversight."
OL,16,FA Department for Work and Pensions
OL,17,F(DWP) spokesperson said: "As pension
OL,18,Fschemes grow, we want to ensure that
OL,19,Fsavers continue to receive the best
OL,20,Fpossible outcomes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@gO]yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777341846
OL,3,CStudy highlights 'extraordinary
OL,4,Cconsolidation of power' in pensions
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"Our consultation explored exactly the
OL,8,Fquestions this report raises,
OL,9,Fexamining how existing governance
OL,10,Fstructures and regulatory frameworks
OL,11,Fneed to evolve as the market
OL,12,Fconsolidates.
OL,14,F"We are carefully considering all
OL,15,Fresponses and will set out next steps
OL,16,Fin due course."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
